167static const struct gf100_gr_func
168gk208_gr = {
169 .init = gk104_gr_init,
170 .mmio = gk208_gr_pack_mmio,
171 .fecs.ucode = &gk208_gr_fecs_ucode,
172 .gpccs.ucode = &gk208_gr_gpccs_ucode,
173 .ppc_nr = 1,
174 .grctx = &gk208_grctx,
175 .sclass = {
176 { -1, -1, FERMI_TWOD_A },
177 { -1, -1, KEPLER_INLINE_TO_MEMORY_B },
178 { -1, -1, KEPLER_B, &gf100_fermi },
179 { -1, -1, KEPLER_COMPUTE_B },
180 {}
181 }
182};

184int
185gk208_gr_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index, struct nvkm_gr **pgr)
186{
187 return gf100_gr_new_(&gk208_gr, device, index, pgr);
188}
